<法規內容>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 1</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[This Standard is prescribed in accordance with the provisions of Article 17 of the Act Governing Food Safety and Sanitation.]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 2</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[Canned foods packed in metallic containers shall pass inspection by incubation test (37oC for 10 days) and free of microorganisms capable of
reproducing under normal storage conditions.]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 3</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[Canned foods packed in retort-pouch shall pass inspection by incubation test (37oC for 10 days) and free of microorganisms capable of reproducing under normal storage conditions.]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 4</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[Canned foods packed in glass bottles shall pass inspection by incubation test (37oC for 10 days) and free of microorganisms capable of reproducing under normal storage conditions.]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 5</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[This Standard shall be implemented at release date.]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
</法規內容>
</法規>
